"You can only edit the email alias on projects where you are the responsible."
msgstr "Solo puedes editar el alias de correo en proyectos donde eres el responsable."

#. module: project_security_roles
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/project_security_roles/models/project_import_guard.py:0
msgid ""
"You can only manage attachments on project records where you are the project"
